<article id="post-1750406" class="post-1750406 page type-page status-publish hentry">

	<section class="" style="background-color: #ffffff">
    <div class="container with-header section-text-title">
        <h2 class="text-center">A Nordic media house built on trust</h2>
    </div>
<style>

</style>
<div class="container with-header">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="text-section text-center">
            <p style="text-align: center">What began as a small publishing house in 1839 is now a media house with some of the strongest news brands in the Nordics. Each day millions of  Swedes, Norwegians and Finns interact with Schibsted to be updated, engaged and entertained. On 8 June 2024 we became a stand-alone media company, separated from the marketplace and growth and investment divisions of Schibsted.</p>
<p style="text-align: center">
        </div>
                                        <div class="container text-center">
                    <a href="https://vend.com/"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="button">Go to Vend                    </a>
                </div>
                                            </div>
</div>
</section><section class="" style="">    <div class="divider-section"></div>

